d <- bar_24 %>%
  mutate(date = date(observed)) %>%
  distinct(date) %>%
  nrow()

  group_by(use) %>%
  summarize(n_per_day = sum(number)/d) %>%
  print()

  filter(general_use != "dog_poo") %>%
  group_by(general_use) %>%
  summarize(n = sum(number)) %>%
  print()
